s those sessions have made him think about remixing one of OneRepublic's biggest hits, \\\"Apologize,\\\" saying it would \\\"go crazy right now.\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2663, \"end\": 2674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OneRepublic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OneRepublic\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OneRepublic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OneRepublic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those sessions\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been 17 years, it's time,\\\" he adds.\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"17 years\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to figure out who the right rapper is.\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right rapper\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 I have dropped some hints to Jack [Harlow].\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2861, \"end\": 2865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.9767569612904299, \"rank\": 0.023758717445429206, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some hints\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did a record with 21 Savage last year and I asked his crew, like, 'Does he like \\\"Apologize\\\"?'\\\"\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a record\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"21 Savage\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2905}, {\"ngram\": \"his crew\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And when it comes to re-recording your o